output: Dharmik Unagar is a Full Stack Developer with 6+ years of experience in web development. He has experience and knowledge in both Back-End and Front-End development of websites and applications. Dharmik has worked with various frameworks and technologies such as MEARN, MEAN, PHP (Laravel, Codeigniter, WordPress), TypeScript, React.js, Redux, Vue JS, jQuery, MongoDB, MySQL, Firebase, PostgreSQL, Node.js, Express.js, and Laravel. He has good communication and planning skills and enjoys taking on complex projects and finding the best solutions. Dharmik has worked on projects like Render Health and Veg King, where he has contributed to the development of various scopes such as super admin, admin, hospital, doctor, patient, buyer, seller, and admin. He holds a BCA and MCA degree and is familiar with tools like Atlassian Jira, GitHub, GitLab, Asana, Bitbucket, Heroku, UI/UX, Figma, Photoshop, Logo, and Post.
